title: 167 Alan Dart Knitting Patterns
description:
This torrent includes the 110 Alan Dart patterns that are already posted here on Pirate Bay. It also includes the ones from the 2006-2012 Simply Knitting magazines that were recently posted. Other personal files have been added.

I am posting this collection because I had it in some private web space but someone reported it to the fine people at Alan Dart. They, in turn, asked me to take my files down. Those files were seen by about 10 people. Now hundreds, possibly thousands, will be able to have these files. Enjoy!
